    "These evaluation metrics effectively indicate whether the model has the potential to be beneficial in actual diagnostic settings by accurately identifying the limits of polyps.",
    "We will discuss three categories of results: the individual performance of integrated CNN models, the combined CNN + DWT and CNN + DWT + SVM models' performance, and the semantic segmentation results.",
    "We conduct a comparative analysis to identify the system's strengths and weaknesses in comparison to others.",
    "Figures and comparisons are employed.",
    "The point of this paper was to carefully look at every part of the suggested PolynetDWTCADx system to see if it could successfully improve the ability to find and separate colorectal cancer."
